   in the same universe as `A`. `Prop` can be mapped into other universes using `ulift` 
   and `prop_resize`, if we assume the resizing axiom. -/
@[hott]
def Subset (A : Set.{u}) := A -> trunctype.{u} -1
   
@[hott]
